{"tid":164614,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[小知識] 點解18歲=成人？","createTime":"2017-03-20T19:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T04:12:02.000Z","uid":89368,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4f1f2df999c4797d679e509f12d3e48b441bd4","tid":164614,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:38:20.000Z","msg":"人類世界大多數國家及地區法律訂立18歲為成年標準。一旦當地居民達至18歲，就可以享有各種相應權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">但點解會係18歲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n其實本來<span style=\"color: pink;\">21歲</span>先係是過往歐美國家嘅成年標準，係21歲之後，就可以履行各種相應權利，並承擔相關義務。<br />\n<br />\n但到左第二次世界大戰後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，為左加快社會的發展，大部分國家都紛紛將成年標準下調至18歲，而到了左依家，甚至有國家更進一步提出將成年標準再下降至16歲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d72d7aa4d9352d6f2ebfb3f963aa316f9f6709","tid":164614,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:41:06.000Z","msg":"咁點解係21歲？"},{"pid":"90eb2d8f5c2dd6f7566757439a3e2bcfde06e0f6","tid":164614,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:44:34.000Z","msg":"以前啲女人平均21歲破處<br />\n跟住打完仗啲後生性慾旺盛女人平均18歲破處<br />\n而家啲人唔忍得16歲一夠秤就破。。。"},{"pid":"358ede7ed51c359ff758543a520d2ac143b78960","tid":164614,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:46:37.000Z","msg":"點解21歲=成人？"},{"pid":"efd9ffdb6c8be9f08275939b8ab4ed2fe3582ba7","tid":164614,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解係21歲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n21果下相信當時都係求撚奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c654dd9b06b43303b5d629e5e19fad9a77abe3","tid":164614,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點解係21歲？</blockquote><br /